             {"text": "Initiate a graceful shutdown sequence to avoid corruption, even though it takes longer", "consequence_if_chosen": "The graceful shutdown takes four minutes — by the time the hosts power down, vssadmin has already finished deleting shadow copies on all 26 targeted hosts"},
