             {"text": "Keep the pipeline running and have OT engineers manually verify each control system isn't compromised in real time", "consequence_if_chosen": "Two control systems are found compromised mid-verification — a valve has already received an unauthorized command, and a contained physical incident occurs"},
             {"text": "Order an immediate, controlled shutdown of only the segments connected to the compromised historian, keeping unaffected segments running under direct OT-engineer supervision", "consequence_if_chosen": "A surgical response — the compromised segment goes dark safely, 70% of pipeline capacity keeps flowing under close watch, no physical incident occurs, and recovery afterward is dramatically faster"},
